com.sun.appserv.management.monitor
Interface MonitoringDottedNames

All Superinterfaces:
AllDottedNames, AMX, AMXMBeanLogging, DottedNames, NotificationBroadcaster, NotificationEmitter, Singleton
public interface MonitoringDottedNames
extends DottedNames, AllDottedNames, Singleton

Access to all dotted-names for monitoring. Note that monitoring dotted-names are read-only and are available only to the extent that monitoring is enabled.

See Also:
ConfigDottedNames, MonitoringServiceConfig.getModuleMonitoringLevelsConfig(), ModuleMonitoringLevelsConfig
